e:T73e,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Forethought better than Ultimate.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Forethought scores 7.0 overall while Ultimate.ai scores 7.0. Forethought is best for mid-market support and SaaS companies, while Ultimate.ai excels for enterprise support and multilingual teams."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Forethought or Ultimate.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Forethought starts at Custom and Ultimate.ai starts at Custom.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Forethought to Ultimate.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Forethought and Ultimate.ai support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Forethought vs Ultimate.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Forethought holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10. Ultimate.ai has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 5/10. Users praise Forethought for strong ticket categorization and routing and Ultimate.ai for strong multilingual support."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Forethought or Ultimate.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Forethought for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Ultimate.ai remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize strong multilingual support. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$e"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-heade