17:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Forethought and Ultimate.ai share a solid foundation of core features including Live Chat, Ai Chatbot, Knowledge Base, Analytics. Where Forethought pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Ticket Management, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Ultimate.ai uniquely offers Multichannel, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Forethought holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Ultimate.ai scores 7/10 overall and 5/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
18:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Forethought and Ultimate.ai offer flexible pricing models. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
